name: ● Endings
description:
CHILD EX MACHINA

This series of 42 pieces is a recursive man vs machine collab curated GAN outputs ~ a visual narrative of a simulated dream state imaginarium. It defies time and the reality itself, inviting the viewer into an AI collective consciousness ~ singularity. Respecting the entropy of the universe ~ although everything has an end, beginnings are happening too ~ so Birth is split in two complementing pieces. This celestial collaboration with Laurence Fuller features his original poem Birth, written and performed by @laurencefuller
, we celebrate the beginning of life.

Video art by @childish5d
